%% AI request & approval flow (target). See 07-ai-operating-layer.md
flowchart TB
  U[User intent] --> Svc[runAiTask]
  Svc --> RBAC{can role, perm?}
  RBAC -- no --> D403[403]
  RBAC -- yes --> Bud{over budget?}
  Bud -- yes --> D429[429 fail-soft]
  Bud -- no --> Ctx[Context Service\ntenant-scoped + PII redacted]
  Ctx --> Model[Prompt + model routing + retries]
  Model --> Val{schema valid?}
  Val -- no --> D502[invalid_response]
  Val -- yes --> Lvl{action level}
  Lvl -- L0/L1 --> Info[return info/recommendation]
  Lvl -- L2 --> Draft[return draft — human sends]
  Lvl -- L3 --> AQ[ApprovalRequest queue]
  AQ --> Appr{approved?}
  Appr -- no --> Drop[logged, not executed]
  Appr -- yes --> Exec[Action Executor under tenant ctx]
  Lvl -- L4 --> Policy{within policy + cap + kill-switch?}
  Policy -- yes --> Exec
  Policy -- no --> AQ
  Exec --> Log[AiActionLog + rollback consideration]
  Info & Draft & Log --> Tel[Telemetry: tenant, cost, quality, outcome]
